sentences.english: If the abdomen, should take the navel as a center.
sentences.chinese: 若是腹部，應以肚臍眼爲中心。

sentences.english: Dirt gets rolled up in your navel.
sentences.chinese: 泥垢總是積在肚臍眼裏。

sentences.english: As I said, belly button bacteria are personal.
sentences.chinese: 就如我以前說過的，肚臍眼裏的微生物都很有個性的。

sentences.english: When a kitty is hungry, stuck the cat food into one's navel one by one.
sentences.chinese: 貓咪餓的光陰，把貓糧一顆顆卡在自己肚臍眼裏。

sentences.english: A whole ecosystem lives in your belly button.
sentences.chinese: 你的肚臍眼中存在着一整個生態系統。
